;-----------------------------------------------------------
@周回特典_適用
FOR LOCAL,1,CHARANUM
	SIF TCVAR:LOCAL:感度上昇部位
		TALENT:LOCAL:(TCVAR:LOCAL:感度上昇部位) ++
NEXT

